description:
The marketing and growth meetup with industry experts. Learn all about growth hacking strategies and take part in the networking and Q&A sessions.
At June's edition Ana Maria Lima will be talking about "How to Get on Google's First page". She will share secrets and tips on page optimization, keywords and objectives. In this talk she will unveil how can Search Engine Optimization (SEO) help you get that spot on the first page and outrank competitors. Join us and learn about how to drive inbound traffic that could grow your business for years to come.
More about the speaker:Ana Maria Lima is Senior Content Manager at the publisher E-Konomista.pt and responsible for the Editorial Competence Center of Adclick. Se has 10 years of experience in journalism and almost another 10 in digital and institutional communication, in areas like the support for new entrepreneurs and the creation of new companies; city marketing; university management; communication of European Union programs; among many other projects.
name: Let's Grow Again #16
